      "cookedHtml": "<p>I am creating a new item (via <a href=\"http://Make.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Make.com</a>, create an Update module) in a <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> board. I would like to give it an update in the update sections that contains a preformatted table. I am doing this with HTML Code, and it´s working, but somehow it leaves a lot of blank space at the top of the table:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/1/a/1a768201536a4cfcd1b53d357b9ba1f408fd3383.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/1/a/1a768201536a4cfcd1b53d357b9ba1f408fd3383_2_393x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"393\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">953×1212 11.5 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>This is the HTML code:</p>\n<table>\n  <tbody>\n\t<tr>\n\t  <td>Column 1 </td>\n\t  <td>Column 2 </td>\n\t  <td>Column 3 </td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t  <td>1\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td>2\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td>3\n\t  </td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t  <td><br />\n\t  </td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t  <td><b